setupJokes.setup: A bear walks into a bar and says, “Give me a water and … cola.”
setupJokes.pun: “Why the big pause?” asks the bartender. The bear shrugged. “I'm not sure; I was born with them.”

setupJokes.setup: Why can't you hear a pterodactyl go to the bathroom?
Why did the frog take the bus to work today?
What breed of dog can jump higher than buildings?
setupJokes.pun: Any dog, because buildings can't jump.

setupJokes.setup: Why aren't koalas actual bears?
Where do you find a cow with no legs?
Road work ahead?
What type of sandals do frogs wear?
What do you call a fish with no eyes?
Two guys walk into a bar.
What do you call an alligator in a vest?
A man walks into a pet store and asks for a dozen bees. The clerk carefully counts 13 bees out onto the counter.
setupJokes.pun: “That's one too many!” says the customer. The clerk replies “It's a freebie.”

setupJokes.setup: What did the horse say after it tripped?
setupJokes.pun: Help! I've fallen and I can't giddyup!

setupJokes.setup: What do you call a pile of cats?
I ordered a chicken and an egg online.
setupJokes.pun: I'll let you know what comes first.

setupJokes.setup: Why do seagulls fly over the sea?
setupJokes.pun: If they flew over the bay, they would be bagels.

setupJokes.setup: Why should you never play poker at the zoo?
Which is faster, hot or cold?
setupJokes.pun: Hot, because you can catch cold.

setupJokes.setup: What's black and white and goes round and round?
setupJokes.pun: A penguin in the washing machine.

setupJokes.setup: What do you call a boomerang that won’t come back?
My uncle named his dogs Timex and Rolex.
Fun fact: Australia's biggest export is boomerangs.
What's the best thing about Switzerland?
setupJokes.pun: I don't know, but its flag is a big plus!

setupJokes.setup: My new thesaurus is terrible.
setupJokes.pun: Not only that, it's also terrible.

setupJokes.setup: What did the buffalo say when his son left?
What do you call a boomerang that won’t come back?
How do we know that the ocean is friendly?
Did you hear about the first restaurant to open on the moon?
setupJokes.pun: It had great food, but no atmosphere.

setupJokes.setup: Do you want to hear a construction joke?
setupJokes.pun: Sorry, I'm still working on it.

setupJokes.setup: Why do ducks have feathers?
How do you measure a snake?
You heard the rumor going around about butter?
setupJokes.pun: Never mind, I shouldn't spread it.

setupJokes.setup: What's a pirate's favorite letter?
setupJokes.pun: You probably think it's “R” but it be the “C”.

setupJokes.setup: How much teddy bears never want to eat anything?
I can never take my dog to the park because the ducks keep trying to bite him.
setupJokes.pun: I guess that's what I get for buying a pure bread dog.

setupJokes.setup: I stayed up all night and tried to figure out where the sun was.
